  %h1 Venue
  %p
    Our wedding will take place at 
    %a{:href => "http://www.dewsall.com", :alt => "Dewsall Court", :target => "_blank"} Dewsall Court
    in Herefordshire, a stylish family home. Weather permitting, the ceremony will take
    place in the garden outside the house. If we must, we'll hold the ceremony indoors.
  %p
    %img.shadow-large{:alt => "Dewsall", :src => "images/dewsall-mansion.png"}/
