  %h2 Address
  %p
    Dewsall Court,
    Callow,
    Hereford,
    United Kingdom,
    HR2 8DA.

  %h2 By car
  %p
    Take M4, or A40, or M40, it will take around 3 hours in any case if you don't get lost (it happened to Evgeny when he was driving there for the first time). Google has
    %a{:href => "https://maps.google.co.uk/maps?saddr=london&daddr=hr2+8da&hl=en&sll=51.528642,-0.101599&sspn=0.593777,1.672668&geocode=FYfwEQMdPQ3-_yl13iGvC6DYRzGZKtXdWjqWUg%3BFTV0GQMd6AfW_ynZER2EVzVwSDEq4Q6hgZMbFQ&mra=ls&t=m&z=9"} driving directions
    for your convenience.
  %h2 By train
  %p
    A June timetable is not available yet but there should be a train from Paddington to Hereford that will take about 3 hours. Then you can take a taxi: Dewsall is only 6 miles away from the station.
  %h2 By helicopter
  %p
    For the venture capitalists among the guests, there is a helicopter pad at Dewsall.
